
How to prepare the Raspberry Pi 3 for EcoSoft

1. Downlaod and flash armbian to the raspberry pi : https://www.raspberrypi.org/downloads/raspbian/

2. Update the system and isntall libconfig:
    $ sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get upgrade
    $ sudo apt-get install pkg-config libconfig-dev libconfig++-dev

3. If necessary install wiringpi
